{"tid":1936614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自從兩年前打完個山竹，香港社會就冇再平靜過","createTime":"2020-03-21T10:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T13:38:55.000Z","uid":123613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8075c0a503e79bd01dcc8cd4d26465e843068642","tid":1936614,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:26:14.000Z","msg":"兩年前9月16日超強十號風球山竹襲港 相信大家都仲記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「返工」篇：<br />\n山竹之後嗰日<br />\n四線齊冧<br />\n中環站撞車<br />\n85三罷<br />\n蒙面法全線停駛<br />\n雙11三罷<br />\n<br />\n「賣港篇」：<br />\n高鐵通車<br />\n港珠澳大橋通車<br />\nHardsell明日大嶼<br />\n逃犯條例<br />\n721<br />\n831<br />\n武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n好多人覺得上年六七月社會先開始唔平靜 其實2018年9月16日打完山竹之後香港社會就再冇平靜過 以上咁多事件就係全方位測試全港市民嘅底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fd5cc2262e88797da5795f2dfeeb2de64c9147","tid":1936614,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"竹竹，我懷念你"},{"pid":"d2bde19cc4113399d87cf009f4925d92f39cffbe","tid":1936614,"uid":104138,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"應該係自回歸以後就無平靜過"},{"pid":"fdc5eaba1e2655b451ba8eb7aaf2e810a1f1d005","tid":1936614,"uid":118520,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2bde19cc4113399d87cf009f4925d92f39cffbe","tid":1936614,"uid":104138,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"應該係自回歸以後就無平靜過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"1842年以來冇平靜過"},{"pid":"4913c9fee66368eced250c52c318728c53b2b21d","tid":1936614,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e625df9179166f7b2f9d40155b564300a936946a","tid":1936614,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T13:38:55.000Z","msg":"自從柒婆之後<br />\n香港人覺醒就真"}]}